CreateTicket:
*Welcome to ticket room*
*To create a ticket, please use the format below:*

*bet,codes/stack/username/confirmation message* 

Example
*bet,a24703,by24905,h25212/100/stiles/Transfer Confirmation. RTGS$220 to da stiles Approval Code: PP225122.1311.G63213. New wallet balance: RTGS$ 424.93.*

If you have already have money in your account, dont put confirmation message.

Example
*bet,a24703,by24905,h25212/100/stiles*

To create multiple tickets at the same time use *next* to seperate the tickets and put username and confirmation message at the end.

Example Bets,a24703,h25212/140/next/a25703,h24212/100/next/a24743,h25312/400/stiles/Transfer Confirmation. RTGS$220 to da stiles Approval Code: PP225122.1311.G63213. New wallet balance: RTGS$ 424.93.

developed by *charles madhuku*
